name: HIMP
description: The service of our application is to choose the option closest to the plan of the room (kitchen, living room, bedroom, etc.) to be decorated, to determine the price range, to choose the furniture you are looking for, to place the decoration in your mind in your home, to decide and to make the purchase. A service that consists of sending the furniture you purchase to you in the form of cargo. Thus, instead of going from place to place, you will be able to take the phone in your hand and make the most suitable decoration for your home.
